 * interval will be \( [a, b] = [l_1, u_1] \). If different signs are found at a later
 * iteration {@code k>1}, then the returned interval will be either
 * \( [a, b] = [l_{k+1}, l_{k}] \) or \( [a, b] = [u_{k}, u_{k+1}] \). A root solver called
